tweet: On behalf of my staff and the entire Luetkemeyer family, I wish everyone in Missouri-03 a Merry Christmas! http://bit.ly/2EPZj9c

Along with my fellow Americans, I send my sincere condolences to the entire Bush family on this difficult day. We all gain some comfort in knowing he is now reunited with his beloved wife, First Lady Barbara Bush.

America has lost an honorable man who leaves a legacy of conservative leadership. President George H.W. Bush exemplified the Greatest Generation through his faithful commitment to our nation as a war hero, Congressman, Ambassador to the UN, Director of the CIA and President.
